raw_html:
Privacy Policy
At TreeCardGames, the privacy of our users and visitors is of extreme importance to us. TreeCardGames is committed to ensuring that your privacy is protected.
What information do we collect?
We don't collect any personally identifiable information about you. When using this website, you are not required to provide us with any personally-identifying information.
When you subscribe to our newsletters your name and email address will be used only for this purpose and you may unsubscribe at any time. TreeCardGames does not sell or rent your private information (name and email address) to anyone.
This website also links to other sites and contains advertisements of third parties. We are not responsible for their privacy policies or how they treat information about their users.
Cookies
This website does not use cookies but some of our third party links and advertisers do. Cookies are used to customize the advertising and content you see in a website.
Ads appearing in our website are provided by Google. They are used in the following way:
- Third party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on a user's prior visits to our website.
- Google's use of the DoubleClick cookie enables it and its partners to serve ads to our users based on their visit to our sites and/or other sites on the Internet.
- Users may opt out of the use of the DoubleClick cookie for interest-based advertising by visiting
Ads Settings.
Your Consent
By using this website, you consent to our privacy policy.
Changes to our Privacy Policy
If we decide to change our privacy policy, we will post those changes on this page.
Contacting Us
If there are any questions regarding this privacy policy you may contact us using the following link: 
www.solsuite.com/support.htm
This document was last updated on June 1, 2015.
